label: ABC4D_tP14_129_c_c_2cf_c-001
title: AgLaTiO$_{4}$ Structure
comments:
(Toda, 1995) report this structure in setting 1 of space group $P4/nmm$ \#129.  We used AFLOW to transform it into the standard setting 2.  This shifted the origin by (a/4 a/4 0). 
 ICSD lists the compounds A$_{2}$MO$_{3}$H (A = alkaline earth, M = metal, H = halide) under this structure type, but we have moved those to a new prototype, \href{current_web_home_dir/A2BCD3_tP14_129_2c_c_c_cf-001}{Ba$_{2}$InO$_{3}$F}.
